<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786000' id='t-786000'>with something as simple</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788000' id='t-788000'>as an oral polio vaccine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791000' id='t-791000'>then pretty soon,</span>
