<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797000' id='t-797000'>every single year.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>There's absolutely no question.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
