<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1300000' id='t-1300000'>But the interesting thing is, of those three,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1302000' id='t-1302000'>India's looking real good, as you just saw in the data.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1304000' id='t-1304000'>And Afghanistan, Afghanistan, we think</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1306000' id='t-1306000'>has probably stopped polio repeatedly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1308000' id='t-1308000'>It keeps getting reinfected.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1310000' id='t-1310000'>So the tough ones: going to get the top of Nigeria finished</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1312000' id='t-1312000'>and getting Pakistan finished.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1314000' id='t-1314000'>They're going to be the tough ones.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
