<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1363000' id='t-1363000'>So good luck. We're all in this with you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1365000' id='t-1365000'>Thank you. (BA: Thank you.)</span>
